data.description: Possible Assumable FHA loan with these 2 units.  This tastefully remodeled single story low maintenance home offers a unique opportunity with income potential from a fully permitted in-law unit with a separate address. The kitchen is a showstopper with quartz countertops & upscale stainless appliances.  SAVE on energy costs w a quality Sunnova Solar System & electric vehicle charging station. A NEW mini-split HVAC system will keep you comfortable year-round. The upgrades continue w new doors & windows, new electrical panel, copper pipe plumbing, a Ring / camera security system, & whole house water filter.    Close to Costco Gateway Plaza with new City Sports Club featuring indoor lap pool. Also, waterfront restaurants in Benicia, SF Ferry Terminal, Mare Island Brewery & kayak access. No Mello-Roos Assessment Tax or HOA.
